### Risk

Low. Pure refactor; no behaviour change visible to callers of `KanbanBackend::persistence_metadata`. The single concern is making sure both backends route their cache updates through the new helper — caught by the existing test suite (any backend that forgets to refresh on flush fails `test_*_backend_exposes_metadata_after_flush`).

