## Where, Why, How

**Where.** Card-mutation handlers in `crates/kanban-tui/src/handlers/card_handlers.rs` repeat the same nested-guard + command-build + execute + error shape ~8 times. The pyramid-of-doom structure:

```rust
pub fn handle_toggle_sort_order_key(&mut self) {
