2. Add `pub use backend::Backend;` to `crates/kanban-core/src/lib.rs`.
3. Add inline tests (see Tests).
4. `cargo build -p kanban-core && cargo test -p kanban-core backend`.

## Edge cases
- `async-trait` object safety: the trait has no Self-by-value methods and no Self-returning methods. The associated `Snapshot` type is OK for object safety as long as trait objects spell it out (`dyn Backend<Snapshot = T>`). The unit tests must include the trait-object cast to catch regressions.
- `with_transaction` takes `&mut dyn FnMut() -> CoreResult<()>` (not `impl FnMut`) to stay object-safe.

