## Motivation
With `kanban_core::Backend` defined and `InMemoryStore` implementing it, `KanbanBackend` in kanban-service can shed its duplicated lifecycle methods and inherit them from the core trait. The kanban-specific surface stays: `as_data_store()` and `persistence_metadata()`.

## Current state
`crates/kanban-service/src/backend.rs:25-82`:
```rust
